# README sync

When your change affects **architecture, integrations, routes, major views, or documented behavior**, update the repository root **`README.md`** in the same change when practical.

Follow the project Cursor skill **readme-maintenance**: read `.cursor/skills/readme-maintenance/SKILL.md` and `.cursor/skills/readme-maintenance/reference-scan-checklist.md`, then patch only stale sections. Do not add unverified middleware or paste secrets.
